  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tales Beyond The Tomb</strong> is an episodic horror series that immerses players in the shadows of real-life cases.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired by the atmospheric horror of the '80s and '90s, each episode recreates terrifying experiences lived by real people, blending nostalgia with relentless suspense.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This is the third episode in the series:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416690/extras/aee4663ba4fb2ac521f0cb7923febce7.poster.avif?t=1753938190\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416690/extras/aee4663ba4fb2ac521f0cb7923febce7.webm?t=1753938190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416690/extras/aee4663ba4fb2ac521f0cb7923febce7.mp4?t=1753938190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Episode 3: The Last Vigil</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nick Harrison, the new night guard at Guadalupe Cemetery, believes he’s taking on a quiet night shift. However, as darkness falls, he quickly realizes he’s gravely mistaken. The cemetery holds more than just the dead.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VHS Aesthetic:</strong> A throwback to the classic horror films of the '80s and '90s with nostalgic visuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Photorealistic Graphics and Immersive Environments:</strong> Detailed scenes that heighten tension and immersion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player Voice Interaction:</strong> Microphone-enabled gameplay for an even scarier experience (microphone optional).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Text-Based Dialogue System:</strong> Dynamic narratives delivered through engaging dialogues.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic Driving:</strong> Fully physics-based car driving system.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first-person exploration experience where realism is key. Navigate mysterious locations, face your darkest fears, and uncover disturbing truths hidden in the shadows of real-life cases.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tales Beyond The Tomb</strong> is an episodic horror series that immerses players in the shadows of real-life cases.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired by the atmospheric horror of the '80s and '90s, each episode recreates terrifying experiences lived by real people, blending nostalgia with relentless suspense.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This is the third episode in the series:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416690/extras/aee4663ba4fb2ac521f0cb7923febce7.poster.avif?t=1753938190\" width=590 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416690/extras/aee4663ba4fb2ac521f0cb7923febce7.webm?t=1753938190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416690/extras/aee4663ba4fb2ac521f0cb7923febce7.mp4?t=1753938190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Episode 3: The Last Vigil</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nick Harrison, the new night guard at Guadalupe Cemetery, believes he’s taking on a quiet night shift. However, as darkness falls, he quickly realizes he’s gravely mistaken. The cemetery holds more than just the dead.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VHS Aesthetic:</strong> A throwback to the classic horror films of the '80s and '90s with nostalgic visuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Photorealistic Graphics and Immersive Environments:</strong> Detailed scenes that heighten tension and immersion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player Voice Interaction:</strong> Microphone-enabled gameplay for an even scarier experience (microphone optional).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Text-Based Dialogue System:</strong> Dynamic narratives delivered through engaging dialogues.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic Driving:</strong> Fully physics-based car driving system.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first-person exploration experience where realism is key. Navigate mysterious locations, face your darkest fears, and uncover disturbing truths hidden in the shadows of real-life cases.</p>",
